messages.message:
Sharing some positive feedback for a change :slightly_smiling_face:

In the *last 10 mins,* I created a custom app using Build which extracts the desired key fields from trust docs using the *3 samples* shared by the Dynasty team. (more context of their use case here (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1oJaAIRMUNtPYc9MGkq1Pg_lwfaXd_6gt2_Q983cYGk4/edit#heading=h.p3921cc0cevp)) The initial results look very good (see the screenshots). We will take this back to the Dynasty team to validate and try on a larger set of documents.

There are a lot of things to improve on AI Hub (keep your feedback coming!). This example is a reminder of the massive value we can unlock for potential customers with AI Hub. Looking forward to the diversity of use cases we would see in the coming weeks.

Onwards! :muscle::skin-tone-2:
